{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "最后一战。傅红雪在九华山与公子羽决斗。如意大师作为第四位见证人出场，傅红雪与她以地藏菩萨典故对答，获得内心安宁。傅红雪走上石台，一刀击败公子羽，面具碎裂露出燕南飞真面目。燕南飞承认是公子羽替身，请求傅红雪出手被拒后自尽。卓夫人揭示铜镜后的老人才是真正公子羽。真正的公子羽因欲望衰老，一直寻找替身维持权力。傅红雪拒绝成为公子羽，宁愿做回自己。公子羽宣布退隐，傅红雪在孔雀山庄废墟前放下讣闻，最终与明月心重逢。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这位就是名满天下的傅红雪施主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "是的，我就是傅红雪。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "大师驻锡九华，想不到居然也知道傅大侠的名声。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "贫僧虽然身在方外，对江湖中的事，却并不十分生疏。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "大师以前是不是见过他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "仿佛见过一次，只是那时天色昏黑，并没有看清楚。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "大师虽然看不清他，他却一定看清了大师的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "因为这位傅大侠是夜眼，在黑暗中视物，也可以明察秋毫。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "大师来自何处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "来自九华。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "王子来自何方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "来自新罗。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "他舍弃尊荣，为的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "舍身学佛。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "既然舍身学佛，为何誓不成佛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "只因普渡众生。",
      "tone": "庄严",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "王子于今何在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "仍在九华。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "王子普渡众生，大师呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "贫尼亦有此愿。",
      "tone": "庄严",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "既然如此，但望大师赐福，使我心清宁安静。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你有何愿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "安忍不动如大地，静虑深密如秘藏。",
      "tone": "庄严",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "好，你去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "是，我去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在我已知道了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "知道是你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你还知道什么？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "该知道的都已知道。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你……你怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "静虑深密如秘藏。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在你已随时可以拔刀。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你能不能再等一等？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我可以等，只不过无论再等多久，胜负也不会有所改变的。",
      "tone": "讥诮",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你已败过一次，何必再来求败？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你几时知道的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "不久。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你拔刀时就已知道是我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以你已有了必胜的把握。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "因为我的心中已不乱不动。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你当然应该有把握，因为我本就应该死在你手里。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "请，请出手。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "现在你的心愿已了？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "那么你现在就已是个死人，又何必我再出手？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "施主胜了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "大师真的如意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "text": "既然大师也未必如意，又怎知我是真的胜了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yi_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "如意大师",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，是胜是负，是如意，是不如意，又有谁知道？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "胜就是胜。胜者拥有一切，负者死，这却是半点也假不得的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在燕南飞已死，你当然已……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在燕南飞已死，公子羽呢？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "燕南飞就是公子羽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "真的是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "难道不是？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "决不是。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "是铜镜。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "镜中还有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "看见了我自己。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那么你就看见了公子羽，因为现在你就是公子羽。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你绝顶聪明，从如意大师替你擦油在手上，就猜出昨夜的女人不是她，是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以现在你一定也能想得到，为什么你就是公子羽。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在我真的就是公子羽？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "至少现在是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "要到什么时候才不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "直到江湖中又出现个比你更强的人，那时……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "那时我就会像今日之燕南飞。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，那时你非但不是公子羽，也不再是傅红雪。那时你就已是个死人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是我相信十年之内江湖中决不会再出现比你更强的人，所以现在这一切都已是你的，你可以尽情享受所有的声名和财富，也可以尽情享受我。",
      "tone": "妩媚",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "你永远是公子羽的女人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "永远是。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "谁知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "为什么我知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "因为你才是真正的公子羽。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "公子羽所拥有的名声权力和财富，决不是容易得来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "一个人对自己已经拥有的东西，一定很舍不得失去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "只可惜你已老了，体力已衰退，你要想保持你所拥有的一切，只有找一个人代替你。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "你要找的，当然是最强的人，所以你找上了燕南飞！",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他的确很强，而且还年轻。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "所以他经不起你的诱惑，做了你的替身。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他本来一直做得很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "只可惜他败了，在凤凰集，败在我的刀下。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "对他说来，实在很可惜。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "对你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "对我一样。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "既然已经有更强的人可以代替他，我为什么还要找他？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是我答应他，只要他能在这一年中击败你，他还是可以拥有一切！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我是要他击败你，并不是要他杀了你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "因为你要的是最强的人。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "他认为我的刀法中，最可怕的一点就是拔刀。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以他苦练拔剑。只可惜一年后他还是没有把握能胜你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "所以他更想得到大悲赋和孔雀翎。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以他错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "这也是他的错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "因为他不知道这两样东西早已在我手里。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他也不知道，这两样东西根本没有传说中那样可怕，他纵然能得到，还是未必能有取胜把握。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我早已看出你比他强，因为你有种奇怪的韧力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你能忍受别人无法忍受的痛苦，也能承受别人无法承受的打击。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "所以这一战你本就希望我胜。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以我才会要卓子陪你。我不想你在决战时太紧张。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以你现在已是公子羽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "我只不过是公子羽的替身而已。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是你已拥有一切！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "没有人能真的拥有这一切，这一切永远是你的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "所以我现在还是傅红雪。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这一切你都不愿接受？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你看得出我已是个老人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "今年你已有三十五六？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "三十七。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你知道我有多大年纪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "六十？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你不到六十？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "今年我也三十七。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你知不知道我是因为什么老的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "我是个死人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你还可以再考虑考虑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "我不必。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你一定知道我很不愿让你死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可惜我已没有选择的余地。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "我也没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你什么都没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你没有财富，没有权力，没有朋友，没有亲人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "我只有一条命。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你还有一样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "还有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "声名。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你好像什么都有。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你有财富，有权力，手下的高手如云。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我要杀你，也许并不需要他们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你什么都有，只少了一样。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你已没有生趣。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "就算公子羽的声名能永远长存，你也已是个死人。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "没有生趣，就没有斗志。所以你若与我交手，必败无疑。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你若敢站起来与我一战，若能胜我，我就将这一生卖给你，也无怨言。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "可是你不敢，",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你几时才下定决心，肯这么做的？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "直到我真正想开的时候。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 645
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "想开了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "一个人活着是为了什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "人活着，只不过为了自己心安快乐。若是连生趣都没有，那么就算他的声名、财富和权力都能永远保存，又有什么用？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 651
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "我知道公孙屠他们一定活不长的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 661
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 663
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "因为我已在他们心里播下了毒种。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 665
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "毒种？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "那就是我的财富和权力。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "text": "你认为他们一定会为了争夺这些而死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公子羽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line": 673
    }
